Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.70,0:00:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，妳快說!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳會睡在那裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.50,0:00:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是很清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份不明的外人\N在正常時間外侵入校園內
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴重損傷了\N身為重要休憩場所的茂盛草皮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.95,0:00:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在那裡擺出難看的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且陳列那種會污染我們學生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澈的眼睛和感性\N以及倫理的猥褻物品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還挾帶危險物品進來!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.64,0:00:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要求妳對這一切\N給我做一個合理的說明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有在聽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.81,0:00:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇 ．羽 ．舞．衣． 同 ． 學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:00:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先喝杯茶冷靜一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣同學也請用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁熱喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.60,0:01:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.83,0:01:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.93,0:01:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是三年級的神崎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是這裡的副會長，請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.74,0:01:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎人同學!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.74,0:01:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你是副會長\N可不可以請你先別插嘴？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,端正校園的風紀，維護安全\N是我們執行部的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦\N別這麼劍拔弩張嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是看不慣\N這種得過且過主義啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.29,0:01:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為你們這種態度\N不好好管理擾亂校園秩序的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近才會怪事頻傳\N讓我們執行部成員…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘛好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看，你又來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人要與被告進行會面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是被告啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:01:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:01:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.32,0:02:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很擔心妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠洲城同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維護校園安全是執行部的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣沒錯啦，藤乃會長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在應該先為\N鴇羽同學來到本校一事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到高興啊，不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這片朗朗青空裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的心情 飛散灑滿其中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果命中註定的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠是你該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現實卻無法如願以償
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在閃耀光芒的風裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想的羽毛 飄然飛揚落下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣邁向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就這麼美麗地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始奔騰的熱烈心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躍動出跟那一天同樣的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你率真的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能永遠看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2話 秘密的放學後？\N那個叫珠洲城的怎麼這麼跩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討人厭!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近怪事太多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以執行部長的情緒比較高昂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過她也是學生吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們學校對於學生的指導\N也是交由學生會負責
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要目標是由學生\N來為學生進行校園自治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以\N你也是學生會的成員之一？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太適合耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要妳多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是什麼學生會成員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是來幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打雜小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要妳管!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被呼來喚去的下人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉唆!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在船上救起的那個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎完全沒有醒來過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊，那時候在渡輪上…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果又要遇到那種生死關頭\N那才真的叫人吃不消
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.67,0:05:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先聲明\N我可沒有拜託你跟我一起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是，是我多管閒事了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教師辦公室在這裡對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後我可再也不想\N跟妳和那女孩有所牽扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要亂來請自便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你高興!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼才剛說完就碰到這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鴇羽舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇～羽～同～學～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怕癢啊？抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問，有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上是鄰居來增進情感的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起吃午飯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的學生餐廳挺豪華的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這學生餐廳還真不便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？但是味道還不錯\N蠻受歡迎的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛!是國中部的男生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海!這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽同學，他是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弟弟巧海，國中部一年級
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海，她們是我的同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫瀨能葵\N請務必要跟我作朋友喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是原田千繪\N自稱校園萬事通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是情報販子，請多指教啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥\N那時候真的什麼都沒有做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼…妳是在說什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在渡輪上\N跟那個叫做舞衣的!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會有啦!\N別說了，快吃!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得那個叫鴇羽的\N有點不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對在隱瞞些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，渡輪一案\N跟最近校園內的事情應該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，絕對有關聯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的直覺是這麼告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來，藤乃靜留\N帶領的學生會太散漫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事要徹底調查清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給那個茶飯女和茶道和尚\N一點顏色瞧瞧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之，妳聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼奇怪的動靜的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要立刻跟我報告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近校內怪事頻傳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比方說轉學生\N在地上弄出了個神秘圓圈啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活生生的校園七大神秘事件\N感覺上很棒耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還有其他不少事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最新的頭條新聞就是妳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽舞衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問妳\N這個到底是怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，那個長頭髮的女生…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎唷，是玖我夏姬小姐耶\N真難得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還是一樣漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是這間學校的學生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是隔壁班的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過很少來學校就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…鷺澤老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要是做得太過火\N我會很頭痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾殘局可是得相當費心的哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過\N本部那些人或許覺得有事可做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而會更高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘渡輪上還有另外一個人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我也是今天早上才知道\N吃了一驚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賊狸貓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，那個學長\N就再也不練劍道了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷都已經治好了，真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他可是全國大賽的常客呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:10:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點啦，午休很短的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超麻辣炸彈咖哩麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主…主將
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？快現身!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:11:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫子修女，求求妳，請相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像貓怪一樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，簡直就是黑色惡魔\N沒錯，就是惡魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近這種怪事頻傳啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你們一定很不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，要渡過這難關\N並不是那麼困難
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在神的面前跪下就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，一同祈禱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？只要祈禱就好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，只要誠心誠意\N靜下心來祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來，就再也不會\N被無法扼抑的青春衝動所迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而看到不存在的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春的什麼…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詞態改變的話\N句型也會跟著改變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才剛考完試就忘光了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著下一段例句
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,she wrote him a letter
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這句改成被動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…Mr.中村
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一天上課就蹺課
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在這種地方…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞得全身是傷\N我到底在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛有沒有誰經過這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二三，妳有看到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像有隻貓還是什麼的\N往那邊去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是最後一個HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個挺有朝氣的可愛女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然，她還沒覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她或許會有不錯的發展喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機關已經啟動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用熱烈的吻，吻醒睡美人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很中意她喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等哪，我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳肚子餓了對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有材料的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:15:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可以做出\N更像樣一點的東西啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對自己燒飯的功夫\N可是小有自信的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？下午都不在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N你也不知道怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊，等等啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…小命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很多事情想要問妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，妳是從哪裡來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…妳有打算要去哪裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去找出兄長!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃!舞衣，妳是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡其實是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3樓耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不就是讓她給逃了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.65,0:18:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來\N攔住她就沒意義了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來妳沒溺死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.22,0:18:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的!妳這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了那種事情\N竟然還敢大剌剌地來學校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要是我報警的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這所學校幕後勢力的威壓下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察根本無計可施
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.07,0:19:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳很快就會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了…妳是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HiME？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高次物質化能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一番地那些人是這麼稱呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一番地又是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要解說是可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我有種預感\N如果妳們太悠哉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好會讓事情\N一發不可收拾唷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的迷途孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無依者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快一點\N應該會比較好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:19:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上車!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的心臟…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明根本就還沒覺醒…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜蘭!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海!巧海!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走開，妳擋不住的!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請別迷惘」\N這句話我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.86,0:22:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有無法傳達給你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.60,0:22:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過寂寞的笑容搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.87,0:22:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫過傷口 Lonely good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.18,0:22:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連熱情都會讓我痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追尋著永恆的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.69,0:22:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是我的天空 我的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那段燃燒熔盡的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:23:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘記 請你好好記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要收藏在心扉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.41,0:23:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Search for my life\N總有一天還會再相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你那透明的雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.72,0:23:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 走上各自的道路


